{"tid":1473483,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"德法兩國呼籲香港和平對話 並於基本法框架解放衝突","createTime":"2019-08-15T00:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T06:37:21.000Z","uid":133680,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"65bcf372ca1a5f28ce64d0e8b7643ffe61752115","tid":1473483,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:44:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474738-20190815.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474738-20190815.htm&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQegz11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=e5280fd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474738-20190815.htm&h=0668ba4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474738-20190815.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n德國總理默克爾呼籲，通過對話和平解決近期在香港發生的衝突。<br />\n<br />\n默克爾在柏林會見傳媒時表示，必須採取一切措施防止暴力，並在對話框架內尋找解決方案的可能性，又指保障港人自由必須成為對話的核心。<br />\n<br />\n默克爾說，《基本法》保障港人在所謂「一國兩制」的原則下，擁有比內地更大的自由，指言論自由是香港悠久的傳統，對話應在《基本法》的基礎下進行。<br />\n<br />\n另外，法國外長勒德里昂呼籲香港特區政府，重新與示威者展開對話，和平解決現時的社會危機，阻止暴力升級。"},{"pid":"49aaacbefbed90102dff36ff611de2fc14067b85","tid":1473483,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:48:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8daac9b1a0bd5a7fb4133b599f8b517d933082e6","tid":1473483,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663b96c06ae59bf1b39a644b777b586a242bdf6d","tid":1473483,"uid":223664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:55:35.000Z","msg":"德法終於出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285d24d967d64225686bae5a39d11342f92d1500","tid":1473483,"uid":156868,"like":0,"disl